# Security, Performance, Accessibility

- Validate and sanitize **all** external inputs.
- Adhere to **OWASP Top 10** and language-specific secure-coding guides.
- Aim for **O(1) or O(log n)** complexity on critical paths; measure, don't guess.
- UI code must comply with **WCAG 2.2 AA**.